data.name: INSTRUCTIONS.Text
data.value: Select a game mode to Have the STARTGAME button appear. Then write the name of player 1 and click on next. Then do the same for player 2 (If you are playing multiplayer) to start the game. Take turns alternatively to check any of the 9 boxes with your sign. First player to check 3 consecutive boxes wins. You cannot check a box already taken by the other player. If in case all the boxes are checked without any of the two players having being successfull in making the winning combination, the game is said to be a draw. You can see the number of wins of each player along with the number of draws at the bottom. Press RESTART to clear the board midgame and NEW GAME to play all over again.
